com.interpss.core.algo.dclf

Interface IBranchAngleShiftFactor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ContingencyAnalysisAlgorithm, NetGenAdjustAlgorithm, SenAnalysisAlgorithm
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ContingencyAnalysisAlgorithmImpl, NetGenAdjustAlgorithmImpl, SenAnalysisAlgorithmImpl

    public interface IBranchAngleShiftFactor
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'IBranch Angle Shift Factor'. Interface of branch-angle shifting factor calculation methods for an injection bus and a withdraw bus, or a phase-shifting Xformer, for a monitoring branch.
    See Also:
    DclfAlgorithmPackage.getIBranchAngleShiftFactor()
